392px" /></p><p>据报道，约瑟夫·奎因（ <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/gladiator-2">《角斗士 2》</a> 、</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/stranger-things"><em>《怪奇物语</em></a>》）将在导演萨姆·门德斯即将上映的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队</a>传记片中饰演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/george-harrison">乔治·哈里森</a>。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/let-it-be-review-the-beatles-documentary-3754084">《顺其自然》评论：披头士乐队重温他们 1970 年引人入胜的分手文档</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://deadline.com/2024/12/george-harrison-joseph-quinn-the-beatles-films-sam-mendes-gladiator-ii-stranger-things-1236202130/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Deadline</em></a>周四（12月12日）报道称，据业内人士透露，奎因是该角色的主要人选。</p><p>此前有报道称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/paul-mescal-definitely-playing-paul-mccartney-beatles-biopic-ridley-scott-3821155">， <em>《角斗士 2》</em>导演雷德利·斯科特声称保罗·梅斯卡尔将在影片中扮演保罗·麦卡特尼</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ringo-starr">林戈·斯塔尔</a>本人似乎也证实<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ringo-starr-seems-to-conform-barry-keoghan-will-play-him-in-sam-mendes-biopic-3816577">巴里·基奥根将担任鼓手</a>。</p><p>六月，有报道称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sam-mendes-beatles-biopics-have-reportedly-cast-the-fab-four-3763028">门德斯已经选定了这两位演员，哈里斯·迪金森饰演约翰·列侬，查理·罗饰演哈里森</a>。然而， <em>Deadline</em>指出，工作室尚未正式达成这些角色的交易。 </p><figure id="attachment_3822230" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3822230" style="width: 1400px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3822230" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/JosephQuinn-Gladiator2-Getty.jpg" alt="约瑟夫·奎因" width="1400" height="880" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/JosephQuinn-Gladiator2-Getty.jpg 1400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/JosephQuinn-Gladiator2-Getty-400x251.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/JosephQuinn-Gladiator2-Getty-800x503.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp